summary: Transitive downgrade via devel sub-package dependency
description: |
  System repo: foo-1.4 (baseline)
  Pre-installed: foo-1.4 (direct, not from system repo)
  Artifacts: foo-1.1 (includes foo-devel-1.1, which Requires: foo = 1.1)

  Installing foo-devel from the artifact triggers a downgrade of foo from
  1.4 to 1.1.  DNF5 requires --allow-downgrade for this; DNF4 downgrades
  automatically.  The fix must emit --allow-downgrade on DNF5 only.

context+:
  verified_artifact: foo-1.1
  want_devel: "true"
  xfail: "true"

environment+:
  PRE_INSTALLED_PACKAGE: rpms/foo-1.4/foo-1.4*.rpm
  EXPECTED_PACKAGE: foo-1.1
